{"title":"淮河上，有一支古老的曲调","authors":["宋家伟"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":7,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"淮河上，有一支古老的曲调"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宋家伟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“吱呀，吱呀……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漾在河面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘在山坳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在古老的河道上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常常听到一支古老的曲调"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老船工站在祖先"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选定的支点上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"演奏着永不变化的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉重的曲调"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伏下去，伏下去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉起来，拉起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在拉大的夹角中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"填满淳朴和辛劳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在古老的曲调里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延续着艰辛和欢笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“吱呀，吱呀……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"载走红的石榴黄的水稻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"载来大的冰箱小的“电脑”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现代文明哟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"潮水般地涌进这古老的河道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这儿，有爵士音乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也有《拉网小调》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更有那想离离不开、想丢丢不掉的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古老而又悠远的曲调……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}